import React from "react" export default function Stats(props) { let {hp, attack, defense, special_attack, special_defense, speed} = props.Stats return (

HP: {mon.hp}

Attack: {mon.attack}

Defense: {mon.defense}

Special Attack: {mon.special_attack}

Special Defense: {mon.special_defense}

Speed: {mon.speed}

BST: {`${mon.hp + mon.attack + mon.defense + mon.special_attack + mon.special_defense + mon.speed}`}

) }
